The @ultratrailninghai, Discovery race in the 2019 #UTWT circuit joins the 2020 #UTWT circuit ⛰
In 2020, they won't be any discovery races anymore. Thus, the @ultratrailninghai as well as @transjeju and Whaler's Great Route Ultra-Trail® join the general circuit 🔥
📸: @ultratrailninghai
#BecomeAFinisher

‪The Ultra-Trail® World Tour team wishes you Happy Holidays 🎄‬
‪📸: @luis_escobar‬
‪#UTWT #BecomeAFinisher‬

As you know, we are going to discover new races in 2020 🔥
One of them is @goldenringultratrail 🇷🇺 This 100 km race takes place in Suzdal and crosses beautiful UNESCO World Heritage Sites ⛰
📸: @goldenringultratrail
#UTWT #BecomeAFinisher

Who is gonna be the first to register? 🏃‍♂
#UTWT #BecomeAFinisher

🚨 An amazing opportunity for a few lucky people 🚨
The Ultra-Trail® World Tour 2019 awards ceremony, presented by Volvic and the announcement of the 2020 #UTWT circuit, will take place on December 12 in Paris.
We would love to share this with you, so we are offering a few lucky people the opportunity to attend this ceremony and meet and greet some of the elite athletes, race directors, Volvic representatives and other key industry influencers 🔥
To secure your spot, simply subscribe to our account, share this post and comment on this publication!
If you get lucky, you will receive a message in the next few days with all the details 💥
#Volvic #BecomeAFinisher

The Ultra-Trail® World Tour 2019 is now over and we’re gearing up towards 2020! 💥
Over the last 12 months we've had the opportunity to see great athletes compete in the most beautiful races around the world 🔥⛰️
To conclude this amazing year we will host an award ceremony on December 12th, presented by #Volvic. The winners of the 2019 #UTWT's ranking will be rewarded and the 2020 #UTWT circuit will be unveiled 👊
#BecomeAFinisher
